<div class="panel" style="margin-bottom: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px;">
 <h3>Cohort</h3>
 <b>noun</b>
 <ol>
  <li>a group or company: She has a cohort of admirers.</li>
<li>a companion or associate.</li>
<li>one of the ten divisions in an ancient Roman legion, numbering from 300 to 600 soldiers.</li>
 </ol>
</div>
